[COLOR red][B]Version 2.1.93[/B][/COLOR]
[I]They say water is the essence of life. Nah — it's just really well-treated sewage.[/I]
[B]Critical:[/B]
- Fixed unmarking a single episode as watched accidentally removing all watched history for the entire show.

[B]Moderate:[/B]
- Fixed mark watched not working on episodes — checkmarks now appear immediately.
- Removed ability for episodes to not show watched status during certain conditions.

[B]Needed:[/B]
- Added Resync FlickList button under Tools → Database & Cache Maintenance — pulls fresh data from your FlickList account.
- Code cleanup and internal improvements.

