[COLOR red][B]Version 2.1.90 — Stability & Sync Improvements[/B][/COLOR]
[I]This one goes out to all the Geo Metro owners out there. You know who you are.[/I]
[B]Critical:[/B]
- Fixed sync engine not detecting new activity — watchlists, favorites, and watched status now refresh properly.
- Fixed items not being removed from watchlists and favorites.
- Fixed API errors causing crashes instead of retrying gracefully.
[B]Moderate:[/B]
- Fixed date/time handling for international formats.
- Improved cache refresh timing.
[B]Needed:[/B]
- UI polish and label improvements throughout settings and menus.

